<div id="review_2758793227" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2758793227" />
    <a title="Reg Fuller" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/25770511-reg-fuller"><img alt="Reg Fuller" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1553210541p2/25770511.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2758793227?book_show_action=true">Mar 21, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Reg Fuller" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Reg Fuller" href="/user/show/25770511-reg-fuller">Reg Fuller</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2758793227" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3081703179619174632">This is a wonderful devotional. There is a topic that covers most any need that will arise in your daily journey through this life. The part that I most appreciate is the ease of navigation through the book. You can find a devotion by table of contents, topic index, or scripture glossary. I also noted that none of the scriptures repeat throughout the book. This is an encouraging read, and I highly recommend this book.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


