<div id="review_2845276543" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2845276543" />
    <a title="David Huff" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/22679327-david-huff"><img alt="David Huff" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1567382988p2/22679327.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2845276543?book_show_action=true">Jun 03, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="David Huff" class="user" itemprop="url" name="David Huff" href="/user/show/22679327-david-huff">David Huff</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2845276543" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17748004113460768730">Have you ever read a book, and felt that the author was sitting right there at the kitchen table with you, giving you nugget after nugget of wisdom as you and he had a friendly and very meaningful conversation together over coffee?<br/><br/>And did it feel like the author was a trusted, dear friend that you’d known for many years, who genuinely cared about you and your life --- even though you had never met him?<br/><br/>You can have that experience right now by picking up a copy of this great Christian devotional,</span>
  <span id="freeText17748004113460768730" style="display:none">Have you ever read a book, and felt that the author was sitting right there at the kitchen table with you, giving you nugget after nugget of wisdom as you and he had a friendly and very meaningful conversation together over coffee?<br /><br />And did it feel like the author was a trusted, dear friend that you’d known for many years, who genuinely cared about you and your life --- even though you had never met him?<br /><br />You can have that experience right now by picking up a copy of this great Christian devotional, “All My Love, Jesus”, which I highly, highly recommend. Ron Lambros has assembled a rich collection of encouraging words, wise observations, Biblical insights, and personal illustrations that are so very practical and edifying! He has a contagious love for God that is evident on every page.<br /><br />This devotional has a great topical and Scriptural index, rather than following a devotion-by-calendar-day approach, which helps draw the reader to topics that are really needed at the particular moment. Also, each devotional thought is brief – often less than a page – but packed with transformative truths. <br /><br />Don’t miss this fine book: it will encourage your heart, and deepen your love for God!<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="17748004113460768730" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


