      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2754860834" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4313209552937674293">My wife and I start every day with reading devotionals first, and then the Bible. Over the years, we have read many books of devotions. “All My Love, Jesus”, by Ron Lambros, is now our favorite. It is written in an easy-to read format, and the messages are both thought-provoking and inspirational. Ron’s long ministerial experience, and his strong relationship with Christ, are condensed in this excellent collection of devotional messages.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

