<div id="review_2752286456" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2752286456" />
    <a title="Andrea" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9915098-andrea"><img alt="Andrea" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1424828181p2/9915098.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2752286456?book_show_action=true">Mar 16, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Andrea" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Andrea" href="/user/show/9915098-andrea">Andrea</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2752286456" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2706075135334649211">If you’re in the market for a solid, timeless devotional book, this is the one. I thoroughly enjoyed every word of this book, and my favorite feature is that it can be searched several ways through an extensive index. You can start on page 1 and read straight through, or you can search by topic or scripture. Also, the author never uses the same scripture twice, so you’re sure to get a good variety in your daily reading. This would be an excellent book to give to young teenagers who are figuring </span>
  <span id="freeText2706075135334649211" style="display:none">If you’re in the market for a solid, timeless devotional book, this is the one. I thoroughly enjoyed every word of this book, and my favorite feature is that it can be searched several ways through an extensive index. You can start on page 1 and read straight through, or you can search by topic or scripture. Also, the author never uses the same scripture twice, so you’re sure to get a good variety in your daily reading. This would be an excellent book to give to young teenagers who are figuring out how to study the Bible, and it would also make an excellent graduation gift. But people who have studied the Bible all their lives will also appreciate this fresh book. I hope we’ll see more books from this gifted author and experienced minister!</span>
  <a data-text-id="2706075135334649211" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


