<span id="freeTextContainer1415959946211502373">About Ron Lambros<br/>	<br/><br/>Rev. Ron Lambros is the CEO and Founder of Ron Lambros Ministries, Inc., a preaching, teaching and consultation ministry located in Atlanta, Georgia. He has spent the past 41+ years serving in various church ministry staff positions, and has been involved in Christian, faith-based management, broadcasting and production, preceded by 7 years of experience in the corporate radio an</span>
  <span id="freeText1415959946211502373" style="display:none">About Ron Lambros<br />	<br /><br />Rev. Ron Lambros is the CEO and Founder of Ron Lambros Ministries, Inc., a preaching, teaching and consultation ministry located in Atlanta, Georgia. He has spent the past 41+ years serving in various church ministry staff positions, and has been involved in Christian, faith-based management, broadcasting and production, preceded by 7 years of experience in the corporate radio and television industry.<br /><br />Ron came to a saving faith in Jesus Christ on April 15, 1977, and was called to the ministry soon after. He was Ordained into the Gospel Ministry on July 30, 1989.<br /><br />Ron is a highly-experienced and respected executive with a demonstrated successful history in broadcast/media production and strategies, and managing and growing faith-based non-profits. He is skilled in fund-raising and donor development; marketing, branding and social media; A/V technologies; ministry growth and expansion; event management and planning; and team building.<br /><br />He is a strong business development professional with a Bachelor of Science degree (Summa Cum Laude) focused in Business Administration/Broadcast Management. He is a proven leader in church ministry and the faith-based non-profit arena, and is a sought-after speaker, teacher and writer.<br /><br />Most of all, he is a devoted follower of Jesus Christ, a husband of one, father of two and grandfather of six. Ron and his wife, Bridget, reside in the suburbs of Atlanta, GA.<br /></span>
